<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.7">
<l>nontik kiṭanta cuṭalai taṭavi nukarum puḻukkiṉṟic</l>
<l>cintit tiruntaṅ kuṟaṅkuñ ciṟupēy ciramap paṭukāṭṭiṉ</l>
<l>munti yamarar muḻaviṉ ṉōcai muṟaimai vaḻuvāmē</l>
<l>yanti nirutta maṉalkai yēnti yaḻaka ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On the cremation ground feeling the exhaustion of the little demoness who slumbers,</l>
<l>sitting [and] thinking herself without meat to eat, having fingered the pyre that lies in ruin,</l>
<l>without that in front the immortals loose the time in the drum sound,</l>
<l>by twilight, [his] hand raised with fire the Beautiful one is dancing [his] dance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
